<h2>Controls</h2>
<p>Playing our free online solitaire card game for kids is super easy!</p>
<p><strong>Mouse or Touch:</strong> Click or tap on a card, then drag it into an empty space or onto one of the four home piles. Your goal is to build each suit in the correct order.</p>
<p><strong>Keyboard Shortcuts:</strong> Use the arrow keys (← ↑ ↓ →) to move between cards. Press the Space bar to send any valid card straight to its home pile.</p>
<p><strong>Quick Restart:</strong> Want to start fresh? Press 'R' for a brand-new shuffle.</p>
<p>No downloads or installations are needed—just open your browser and start stacking cards. It's perfect for young minds learning strategy and focus!</p>
